Title: 033: Building a Personal Brand in Data Science with Senior Insights Manager Josh Coulson
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with Senior Insights Manager at LinkedIn Josh Coulson. You will hear about the implications of moving into the Gig Economy, learn how to build a personal brand in data science, discuss data democratization across organizations and get insights on how to enhance your career and build better opportunities in the space of data science.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at www.superdatascience.com/33
